Michael Hyatt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Hyatt 0 Charlene "Michael" Hyatt is a British-born American actress. Before her work in film and television, she performed on stages throughout the country, particularly in Ragtime on Broadway. She has played Brianna Barksdale on The Wire, Dr. Noelle Akopian on Crazy Ex-Girlfriend and Detective Sheila Muncie on Ray Donovan. Charlene_"_Michael_"_Hyatt is a_British-born_American_actress .
